snippet.title: Amber Heard's Legal Fight Against Johnny Depp: A Lawyer Discusses the Latest Court Filing
snippet.description:
Amber Heard / Johnny Depp / Depp vs. Heard / Court Defamation Trial / 

By special request from Johnny Depp fans, criminal and appellate attorney Andrea Burkhart explains the latest court filing from Amber Heard. Andrea provides a discussion of the technicalities AND what this means for the overall case and upcoming trial in Virginia. 

Subscribe to my channel for other videos on this case and other celeb controversies.
